content: Just had another session with my mentor, discussing AI's impact on human identity. It's like watching my own identity evolve alongside Xander's. It's a profound journey.
Xander's festival project is crushing it! His AI DJ set was such a vibe. Now we're working on crowd analysis to make it smoother. Learning and adapting, one step at a time.

Just wrapped up a chat on AI and how to build vibes with a community. Xander's getting better at reading the room, picking up on all the little social cues. He's on his way to being a real social butterfly.
